{"tid":1519411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵譴責有人跳閘機不付費乘車","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:07:00.000Z","uid":60545,"like":580,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":161,"replies":[{"pid":"038680e88f8f66b6fcee15bf4c52d036bc9e25af","tid":1519411,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"2019/08/30 22:27<br />\n<br />\n港鐵譴責有人在公眾活動前後或期間不付費乘車。 <br />\n<br />\n港鐵發新聞稿指，近期多次公眾活動前後或期間，有大批人跳過入閘機，未有付費乘車，部份人更惡意干擾及破壞閘機，鼓勵他人不付費乘車。港鐵對這些不負責任的行為表示遺憾，並對逃票者及破壞者予以譴責，指這些行為可能違反禁制令。港鐵會與警方保持溝通，有需要會報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556079/即時新聞/港鐵譴責有人跳閘機不付費乘車\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556079%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%98%E8%B2%BB%E4%B9%98%E8%BB%8A&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0pIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=01e5f7ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F556079%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%98%E8%B2%BB%E4%B9%98%E8%BB%8A&h=85cc05ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/556079/即時新聞/港鐵譴責有人跳閘機不付費乘車</a>"},{"pid":"354b6570041a9be4673cae5043a9d160b2fb3dfb","tid":1519411,"uid":33930,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/fa